name: Sage One UK
description: Add a Sage One Instance to connect your existing Sage account to the Sage Accounting Hub, allowing you to manage contacts, sales invoices, ledger accounts, etc. across multiple Sage Elements. You will need your UK, (version 1) Sage account information to add an instance.
